\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf8 Figure 7:\'a0
\f0\b0 PC1 (26% variance) orders emotions from fear/panic to joy/optimism, while PC2 (15% variance) separates serene/reflective states from angry/playful arousal. Tick labels are only shown for a subset of the bars.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa254\partightenfactor0

\fs25\fsmilli12720 \cf6 \strokec6 We also show the correlation between emotion vector projections onto PC1 and PC2, and their projections onto the valence (\'93pleasure\'94) and arousal axes identified in a human study\'a0\
